---

<section id="expertise" data-screen-label="Expertise" style="position:relative;scroll-margin-top:72px">
	<div style="max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;padding:clamp(64px,9vw,110px) clamp(20px,5vw,56px) clamp(40px,6vw,72px);box-sizing:border-box">
		<div data-reveal>
			<p class="ds-kicker" style="margin:0 0 12px">01 · Expertise</p>
			<h2 class="ds-display-lg" style="margin:0">Three disciplines, one bench.</h2>
			<hr class="ds-rule" style="margin-top:16px" />
		</div>
		<div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(min(270px,100%),1fr));gap:clamp(24px,3.5vw,48px);margin-top:clamp(24px,3.5vw,40px)">
			<article data-reveal style="border-top:1px solid var(--ds-line);padding-top:22px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px">
				<span class="ds-micro" aria-hidden="true" style="color:var(--ds-text-faint)">/ 01</span>
				<h3 class="ds-title" style="margin:0">iOS &amp; Apple platforms</h3>
				<p class="ds-body-sm" style="margin:0;color:var(--ds-text-2);text-wrap:pretty">
					Swift 6, SwiftUI, SwiftData, Vision, RoomPlan, on-device ML. Privacy-first, zero-backend architecture — apps that
					never phone home.
				</p>
				<span class="ds-micro" style="color:var(--ds-text-3);line-height:1.8">Swift 6 · SwiftUI · SwiftData · Vision · RoomPlan</span>
			</article>
			<article data-reveal style="border-top:1px solid var(--ds-line);padding-top:22px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px">
				<span class="ds-micro" aria-hidden="true" style="color:var(--ds-text-faint)">/ 02</span>
				<h3 class="ds-title" style="margin:0">AI agent tooling</h3>
				<p class="ds-body-sm" style="margin:0;color:var(--ds-text-2);text-wrap:pretty">
					Claude Code skills and plugins, MCP servers, token optimization, multi-agent orchestration. Tools that make agents
					cheaper, sharper, faster.
				</p>
				<span class="ds-micro" style="color:var(--ds-text-3);line-height:1.8">Claude Code · MCP · Rust · Python</span>
			</article>
			<article data-reveal style="border-top:1px solid var(--ds-line);padding-top:22px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px">
				<span class="ds-micro" aria-hidden="true" style="color:var(--ds-text-faint)">/ 03</span>
				<h3 class="ds-title" style="margin:0">Full-stack product craft</h3>
				<p class="ds-body-sm" style="margin:0;color:var(--ds-text-2);text-wrap:pretty">
					From Rust CLIs to design systems to App Store releases, shipped solo. The whole stack, one pair of hands.
				</p>
				<span class="ds-micro" style="color:var(--ds-text-3);line-height:1.8">Rust · TypeScript · Design tokens · App Store</span>
			</article>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
